{
  "stem": "1873.3",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I understood that, just at the entrance, finally, the panel cracked, and they find the opening.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they told us to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember, I went out, but I left a shoe inside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember, I was afraid, if they take us to a concentration camp with one-- with one shoe, I-- it could be trouble.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I remember going to this Nazi and asking him if I could go down, pick up my--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He allowed me to pick up the shoe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I picked up the shoe, went out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they took us outside the tannery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were-- we were surrounded by a couple of Nazis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Polish people were all around, looking.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this time, again, I managed, actually, to go out from this encirclement and mingle with the people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was barefoot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was looking like a Pole.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And at that time, I was rather-- rather blond, reddish-blond, lighter hair.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The nose was short, a little bit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, you get old, that nose is growing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I didn't look typical Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mingled.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And now I know I must hide, because, any minute, somebody will denounce me or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So I notice a-- a-- a schoolmate of mine, Janek Knopczek.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I told him, Janek, hide me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Please, help me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He said, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was many times in our home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He eat in our place.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He slept even sometimes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I went to-- he did live nearby.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So he said, go to the barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I go to the barn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There's a big padlock on the barn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "So I can't go in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So I'm looking how to go into the barn to hide, until everything is over, so I could escape to the forest or wherever.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
